        "created_at": "2026-01-29T17:11:34.851Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://signal.org/blog/pinned-messages/\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/a/0/a070fdcafbe5753b5b412f3e5b5c640cff8d0c48.svg\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://signal.org/blog/pinned-messages/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Signal Messenger</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:690/361;\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/1/d/1d7ae402634211ef51b0338153ad166530bf2433_2_690x362.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"E7E7E1\" width=\"690\" height=\"362\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://signal.org/blog/pinned-messages/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Put a pin in it</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Your most frequently asked questions, dinner reservations, and vacation itineraries are already top of mind. Now they can be top of chat as well. In the latest version of Signal rolling out now, you can pin your most important messages to the top of...</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
